            "notes": "The main concept of this deck is to utilize the aggro strategy with Spider-Man 2099 as the commander in Duel Commander 1 vs 1 format. The deck focuses on fast-paced gameplay, controlling the board with a mix of counter spells, removal, and card draw. It includes a diverse mana base to support the casting of a variety of spells, including powerful creatures like Murktide Regent, Snapcaster Mage, and True-Name Nemesis. With a range of efficient instants and sorceries like Lightning Bolt, Cryptic Command, and Counterspell, the deck aims to disrupt the opponent's strategy while building its own threats on the battlefield. The inclusion of cards like Vedalken Shackles and Malcolm, Alluring Scoundrel provide additional versatility and power to the deck."
